- Max.
- Hi.

40:17.110 --> 40:18.938
- How is she?

40:18.981 --> 40:21.201
- Better, but I'm
still concerned.

40:21.244 --> 40:24.683
She needs to be on bed rest
until she stops spotting.

40:24.726 --> 40:26.293
- Okay.

40:26.336 --> 40:29.775
- She can't be put
under any stress--

40:29.818 --> 40:31.298
physical or emotional.

40:31.341 --> 40:34.432
It could hurt her
and the baby.

40:34.475 --> 40:37.347
Understand?

40:37.391 --> 40:39.175
- Yeah.

40:39.219 --> 40:44.093
- ♪ Would you really rush
