♪

41:18.171 --> 41:22.001
- I, um...

41:22.044 --> 41:24.743
I...
[grunts, clears throat]

41:24.786 --> 41:26.135
- Hey.

41:26.179 --> 41:27.920
Remember?

41:27.963 --> 41:30.313
You promised...

41:30.357 --> 41:32.794
to let me in.

